name: Kickboxing
about: Knock out stress and challenge yourself with MIRROR's kickboxing at-home classes that will have you feeling the burn. Punch & kick your way to victory as you move through sweaty, action packed rounds.

name: Boxing
about: Create your own boxing gym at home with MIRROR's online boxing classes for full-body strength and next-level endurance. Learn and perform punch combinations for a sweaty, high-intensity boxing workout or try a Boxing + Strength class combining traditional strength moves with boxing rounds.

name: Cardio + Strength
about: Take your at-home cardio exercises to the next level with MIRROR Cardio + Strength, a weight training take on fast-paced interval classes. In Cardio + Strength classes you'll combine traditional muscle-building moves with shorter cardio bursts.

name: Arms + Abs
about: For days with a focus on upper-body, check out MIRROR's abs and arms workouts for an at-home bodyweight or free weights burn.

name: Sculpt
about: Designed to create lean, toned muscles, MIRROR Sculpt classes combine elements from Barre, Pilates, Strength & Cardio, for a unique fitness experience. Using light weight, high rep work, get ready to feel your muscles burn.
